nautilus-flickr-uploader (0.14.2-1~getdeb1) precise; urgency=low

  * New upstream version
    * Sun Jun 17 2012 Juan J. Martinez <jjm@usebox.net> 0.14.2-1
    - FIX: glitch in the progress bar when moving to the next image
    - FIX: two buttons not marked as translatable
    - FIX: the translation for "Cancel" was missing

    * Sat Jun 16 2012 Juan J. Martinez <jjm@usebox.net> 0.14.1-1
    - FIX: error in the DBUS service enabling the progress bar

    * Sat Jun 16 2012 Juan J. Martinez <jjm@usebox.net> 0.14-1
    - NEW: chunked upload for less memory consumption when uploading
    big files and detailed upload progress
    - NEW: upload bandwidth throttling
    - FIX: small UI tweaks
    - FIX: configuration file converted to XML, YAML dependency will
    be removed in next version
    - FIX: set configuration file permissions to 0600

